JUST IN: DOH records new record-high increase of COVID-19 cases on May 28 with 539 new cases. 

This topped the previous highest uptick of cases recorded last March 31 of 538 cases. 

The total is now at 15,588, with 11,069 active cases. | @DYGalvezINQ https://t.co/hO1Og1mMrq
